@startuml
title Iris IoT Framework - Deployment and Connectivity Flow

actor "IoT Device" as Device
participant "Dock\n(Protocol Listener)" as Dock
participant "Dispatcher\n(Message Router)" as Dispatcher
participant "Input Hook" as InputHook
participant "Thread Pool" as ThreadPool
participant "Handler\n(Data Processor)" as Handler
participant "Output Hook" as OutputHook
participant "Logger\n(Winston)" as Logger
participant "Validator\n(Config)" as Validator

== Initialization & Deployment ==
activate Dispatcher
Dispatcher -> Validator: Validate configurations
activate Validator
Validator --> Dispatcher: Configuration valid
deactivate Validator

Dispatcher -> Dock: Bootstrap and register
activate Dock
Dock -> Dock: Listen on port/protocol
Dock --> Dispatcher: Dock registered
deactivate Dock

Dispatcher -> ThreadPool: Initialize thread pool
activate ThreadPool
ThreadPool --> Dispatcher: Pool ready
deactivate ThreadPool

Dispatcher -> Logger: Initialize logging
activate Logger
Logger --> Dispatcher: Logger ready
deactivate Logger

== Message Processing Flow ==
Device -> Dock: Send IoT message\n(via network protocol)
activate Dock
Dock -> Dock: Parse message to\nJavaScript object
Dock -> Logger: Log incoming message
activate Logger
deactivate Logger

Dock -> Dispatcher: Forward parsed message
activate Dispatcher
Dispatcher -> Logger: Log message routing
activate Logger
deactivate Logger

Dispatcher -> InputHook: Execute input hook
activate InputHook
InputHook -> InputHook: Custom logic\n(pre-processing)
InputHook --> Dispatcher: Modified data
deactivate InputHook

Dispatcher -> ThreadPool: Submit flow job
activate ThreadPool
ThreadPool -> Handler: Execute in thread
activate Handler
Handler -> Handler: Process data
Handler -> Logger: Log processing
activate Logger
deactivate Logger
Handler --> ThreadPool: Processing result
deactivate Handler
ThreadPool --> Dispatcher: Job complete
deactivate ThreadPool

Dispatcher -> OutputHook: Execute output hook
activate OutputHook
OutputHook -> OutputHook: Custom logic\n(post-processing)
OutputHook --> Dispatcher: Final response
deactivate OutputHook

Dispatcher --> Dock: Return response
deactivate Dispatcher

Dock -> Dock: Encode response\n(protocol format)
Dock --> Device: Send response\n(via network)
deactivate Dock

== Hot Reload (Runtime) ==
Dispatcher -> Dock: Hot reload trigger
activate Dock
Dock -> Dock: Swap implementation\n(dynamic reload)
Dock --> Dispatcher: Reload complete
deactivate Dock
deactivate Dispatcher

@enduml
